## LINE Mini App Architecture

### User Flow

1. ユーザーがLINEでQRコードをスキャン
2. LINEミニアプリ起動
3. 商品選択
4. 決済（LINE Pay）
5. ロッカー解錠

---

### System Components

- LINE Mini App (Frontend)
- Backend API (FastAPI)
- Payment (LINE Pay)
- IoT Locker Controller

---

### Data Flow

LINE → API → Locker

---

### Key Features

- No app installation required
- Instant access via QR
- Seamless payment integration
